{"tid":1498021,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陳同佳之亂!  IMF前副總裁預警香港政局不穩 或觸發全球衰退","createTime":"2019-08-23T08:29:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T11:12:26.000Z","uid":72009,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d65dbf767be2e620e30f1ef2885043e2875f49b3","tid":1498021,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T08:29:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-news/NOW.960732/2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Faastocks.com%2Ftc%2Fstocks%2Fnews%2Faafn-news%2FNOW.960732%2F2&d=3B0aCwotxrbiSqfA1QWlArHKdwoo7KeUephkEgg9e70%3D&h=ac3dfa1c\" target=\"_blank\">http://aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-news/NOW.960732/2</a><br />\n<br />\n國際貨幣基金組織(IMF)前副總裁、哈佛大學經濟學家Carmen Reinhart接受《彭博通訊社》訪問時稱，香港持續不斷的政治風波或成為全球經濟的拐點。她表示，全球經濟正受包括中美貿易戰加劇的連串事件衝擊，香港情況屬其主要憂慮。<br />\n<br />\nReinhart稱，香港政局不穩對中國內地及亞洲增長有影響，並不限於地區，而是全球性的影響。她並強調，香港事件可以成為觸發全球經濟大幅放緩，甚至陷入衰退的拐點。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />陳同佳-中出之亂定綠寶之亂好聽<br />\nl"},{"pid":"6d37db0a59219e341df692b628759d5194721115","tid":1498021,"uid":257184,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T08:32:45.000Z","msg":"呢個故事教訓大家，唔好隨便派綠帽"},{"pid":"0d949c0f6d27915d76f799d56cbadd0e7b059bd2","tid":1498021,"uid":39470,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T08:36:12.000Z","msg":"中出引發世界大戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74662f7622693fe2727673ec2eabb6bacffa59b3","tid":1498021,"uid":273703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T08:38:45.000Z","msg":"支持，準備仆街啦支共<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48e53c9460b9a521b0a2ab37e1ee263de89069fd","tid":1498021,"uid":264362,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T08:41:38.000Z","msg":"呢次好好警戒左一眾派帽淫娃，派帽除可致身亡，仲可引發城市大騷動，國際金融危機，戰爭，乃至中共倒台。如令後者發生，請盡力派帽"},{"pid":"6d638936d0f4a4dc13835fd5a43d135c25d0bbca","tid":149